      "вүҲbutВҰ380175"
     ]
    },
    " you say, вҖңHow have you ",
    {
     "type": "char",
     "marker": "add",
     "content": [
      "shown your"
     ]
    },
    " love for us?вҖқ\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "type": "para",
   "marker": "p",
   "content": [
    "вҖңWasnвҖҷt EsawВҰ380181 YacobвҖҷsВҰ380182 brotherВҰ380180?вҖқ declares Yahweh. вҖңYet IвҖҷveВҰ380171 loved Yacob",
    {
     "type": "note",
     "marker": "x",
     "content": [
      {
       "type": "char",
       "marker": "xo",
