   ]
  },
  {
   "type": "para",
   "marker": "p",
   "content": [
    {
     "type": "verse",
     "marker": "v",
     "number": "4",
     "sid": "MAL 1:4"
    },
    "If ",
    {
     "type": "char",
     "marker": "add",
     "content": [
      "EsawвҖҷs descendants in"
     ]
    },
    " EdomВҰ380209 say, вҖңWeвҖҷve ",
    {
     "type": "char",
     "marker": "add",
     "content": [
      "вүҲbeen crushed"
     ]
    },
    ", but weвҖҷll returnВҰ380211 and ",
    {
     "type": "char",
     "marker": "add",
     "content": [
      "вүҲrebuildВҰ380212 what was destroyed"
     ]
    },
    ",вҖқ then army-commanderВҰ380217 Yahweh will say, вҖңThey might buildВҰ380219, but I will tear down. Others will call them вҖҳThe country of wickednessВҰ380225вҖҷ and вҖҳThe peopleВҰ380226 who Yahweh is forever angry with.вҖҷ\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "type": "para",
   "marker": "p",
   "content": [
    {
     "type": "verse",
     "marker": "v",
     "number": "5",
     "sid": "MAL 1:5"
    },
    "Your own eyesВҰ380235 will seeВҰ380236 it, andВҰ380237 youвҖҷll sayВҰ380238, вҖҳYahwehВҰ380240 is greatВҰ380239 even outside YisraelвҖҷsВҰ380243 bordersВҰ380242.вҖҷ вҖқ\n"
