  {
   "type": "para",
   "marker": "p",
   "content": [
    {
     "type": "verse",
     "marker": "v",
     "number": "6",
     "sid": "MAL 1:6"
    },
    "вҖңA son honours his father, and a servantВҰ380248 ",
    {
     "type": "char",
     "marker": "add",
     "content": [
      "вүЎhonours"
     ]
    },
    " his master, ",
    {
     "type": "char",
     "marker": "add",
     "content": [
      "вүҲso"
     ]
    },
    " if IвҖҷm a father, where is my honour? If I am a master, where is my respectВҰ380261?вҖқ says army-commanderВҰ380265 YahwehВҰ380264 to all you priestsВҰ380267 who despise my name.\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "type": "para",
   "marker": "p",
   "content": [
    "вҖңButВҰ380248 you say, вҖҳHow have we despised your name?вҖҷ\n",
    {
     "type": "verse",
     "marker": "v",
     "number": "7",
     "sid": "MAL 1:7"
    },
    "By offering polluted food onВҰ380284 my altarВҰ380280. ButВҰ380283 you sayВҰ380283, вҖҳHow have we polluted you?вҖҷ By sayingВҰ380286 that YahwehвҖҷsВҰ380288 tableВҰ380287 can ",
    {
     "type": "char",
     "marker": "add",
     "content": [
      "just"
     ]
    },
    " be disrespected.\n",
    {
     "type": "verse",
     "marker": "v",
     "number": "8",
     "sid": "MAL 1:8"
    },
    "DonвҖҷt you think itвҖҷs wrong when you sacrificeВҰ380296 blindВҰ380295 animals? IsnвҖҷt it evil when you offerВҰ380294 lame or sick ",
    {
     "type": "char",
     "marker": "add",
     "content": [
      "вүЎanimals"
     ]
    },
    "? Try presentingВҰ380305 them to yourВҰ380314 governorВҰ380307! Will he welcome you or wouldВҰ380313 he ",
    {
     "type": "char",
     "marker": "add",
     "content": [
      "вүҲbe offended"
     ]
    },
    "?вҖқ saysВҰ380315 army-commanderВҰ380317 YahwehВҰ380316.",
    {
     "type": "note",
     "marker": "x",
     "content": [
      {
       "type": "char",
       "marker": "xo",
       "content": [
        "1:8: "
       ]
      },
      {
       "type": "char",
