  },
  {
   "type": "para",
   "marker": "p",
   "content": [
    {
     "type": "verse",
     "marker": "v",
     "number": "10",
     "sid": "MAL 1:10"
    },
    "вҖңYeah, if only thereВҰ380349 was one ",
    {
     "type": "char",
     "marker": "add",
     "content": [
      ">person"
     ]
    },
    " amongВҰ380341 you who would shut the temple gates so that you all couldnвҖҷt ",
    {
     "type": "char",
     "marker": "add",
     "content": [
      "just continue"
     ]
    },
    " to lightВҰ380346 worthless fires onВҰ380341 my altarВҰ380347. I get no pleasureВҰ380352 from you all,вҖқ saysВҰ380354 army-commanderВҰ380356 YahwehВҰ380355, вҖңand I wonвҖҷtВҰ380344 acceptВҰ380360 any offeringВҰ380357 ",
    {
     "type": "char",
     "marker": "add",
     "content": [
      "вүҲthat you all bring me"
     ]
    },
    ".\n",
    {
     "type": "verse",
     "marker": "v",
     "number": "11",
     "sid": "MAL 1:11"
    },
    "People in other countries from the east ",
    {
     "type": "char",
     "marker": "add",
     "content": [
      "all the way"
     ]
    },
    " to the west will honour me, and incenseВҰ380376 and genuine sacrifices will be offeredВҰ380379 to me, because my reputation in those countries will be praised,вҖқ saysВҰ380386 army-commanderВҰ380388 YahwehВҰ380387.\n",
    {
     "type": "verse",
     "marker": "v",
     "number": "12",
     "sid": "MAL 1:12"
    },
    "вҖңButВҰ380392 you all are dishonouring ",
    {
     "type": "char",
     "marker": "add",
     "content": [
      "@my name"
     ]
    },
    " when you sayВҰ380393 that the masterвҖҷsВҰ380395 tableВҰ380394 is polluted, andВҰ380390 that its fruitВҰ380398, its food, can be treated withВҰ380393 contempt.\n",
    {
     "type": "verse",
     "marker": "v",
     "number": "13",
     "sid": "MAL 1:13"
    },
    "You all also say, вҖҳHow tiresome this is,вҖҷ andВҰ380402 you snort at it,вҖқ says army-commanderВҰ380409 Yahweh. вҖңYou all bring ",
    {
     "type": "char",
     "marker": "add",
     "content": [
      "animals"
