    {
     "type": "verse",
     "marker": "v",
     "number": "14",
     "sid": "MAL 1:14"
    },
    "вҖңMay the cheats be cursedВҰ380429 who have maleВҰ380433 animals inВҰ380432 their flocksВҰ380432 and vow to give them, butВҰ380429 instead sacrificesВҰ380435 a second-class animal to the masterВҰ380437! Yes, IвҖҷm a powerful kingВҰ380439,вҖқ saysВҰ380442 army-commanderВҰ380444 YahwehВҰ380443, вҖңand my nameВҰ380445 will be carefully respected among the nationsВҰ380447.вҖқ\n"
   ]
