    {
     "type": "verse",
     "marker": "v",
     "number": "1",
     "sid": "MAL 2:1"
    },
    "NowВҰ380453 you priestsВҰ380453, this commandВҰ380451 is for all of you:\n",
    {
     "type": "verse",
     "marker": "v",
     "number": "2",
     "sid": "MAL 2:2"
    },
    "Army-commanderВҰ380471 YahwehВҰ380470 saysВҰ380469, вҖңIf you all wonвҖҷt listenВҰ380458 and wonвҖҷt ",
    {
     "type": "char",
     "marker": "add",
     "content": [
      "вүҲdecide in your minds"
     ]
    },
    " to honourВҰ380467 to my ",
    {
     "type": "char",
     "marker": "add",
     "content": [
      "вүҲreputation"
