     ]
    },
    ".\n",
    {
     "type": "verse",
     "marker": "v",
     "number": "3",
     "sid": "MAL 2:3"
    },
    "Listen, IвҖҷm aboutВҰ380491 to rebukeВҰ380491 your descendants, and IвҖҷllВҰ380496 spreadВҰ380496 the offal from your festivalsВҰ380502 on your facesВҰ380500, and you all will be takenВҰ380503 away with it.\n",
    {
     "type": "verse",
     "marker": "v",
     "number": "4",
     "sid": "MAL 2:4"
    },
    "ThatвҖҷs so youвҖҷll all knowВҰ380507 that itвҖҷs me who sentВҰ380509 this commandВҰ380512 to you: so that my agreement with the Levites can continue,вҖқ saysВҰ380519 army-commanderВҰ380521 YahwehВҰ380520.",
    {
     "type": "note",
     "marker": "x",
     "content": [
      {
       "type": "char",
